information: The company J. LAMBERT & SÖHNE GMBH & CO. KG, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1832, which operates in the Gardening and horticulture - equipment and supplies industry. It also operates in the Furniture and decorations, garden, and Sowing and planting equipment industries. It is based in Trier, Germany.
